angel.andrsnie.youkr

Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • angel.andrsnie.youkr.Word

  • class Word
extends java.lang.Object
    Word represents a vocabulary word that the user wants to learn. It contains resource IDs for the default translation, Ukr translation, audio file, and optional image file for that word.
